        "message": "LU-2603 obdclass: remove a race between ioctl and release dev\n\nclass_handle_ioctl can touch an obd_device which is now being released\nby class_release_dev. And class_release_dev can release an obd_device\nwhich is now being handled by class_handle_ioctl.\n\nThis patch removes the race by adding proper locking logic\n\nSigned-off-by: Hiroya Nozaki <nozaki.hiroya@jp.fujitsu.com>\nChange-Id: I8c97e128a213f3379664bf6f60615c96df627859\n"
